<br>
mage + cleric + enchanter<br>
<br>
- All can gate which is very nice.<br>
- Depending what you are in the mood for, either the mage pet or enchanter charmed pet can tank<br>
- Mage nukes + Coth (so you don't have to try to AF through a dungeon and have invis wear off at a bad time)<br>
- Cleric heal and rez (obviously)<br>
- Enchanter lull, slow, mez, clarity, charm, and nukes.<br>
<br>
Best of all, you can play all 3 with minimum effort.  Send pet in, hotkey to heal / slow mob / nuke.<br>
<br>
I personally use a mage / cleric duo and have had a lot of success with it.<br>
<br>
Mistress Casala, Arch Convoker of Saryrn<br>
